<center><img src="../g/tree01.jpg" align="top" usemap="#figure1" border=0></center>

<br><br>
<a name="fig2">
The following figure (<a href="help.htm#fig2">Figure #2</a>) is provided to illustrate how the user can move from one image page to another. For any image, the user can switch between unlabeled and labeled versions.
For any image that has a hotspot defined, the user can click in the area to move to an image page of higher magnification. To see all the images for a section, the user should explore all possible branches for each slide in each collection. 
<br>
